cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new architecture for neural machine translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves developing a model capable of abstraction and transfer learning. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training a neural network model. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves developing a framework for efficient development of multilingual NMT.
